      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "In a beautiful review [CITATION_1] ) entitled \"From 'I' to 'L' and back again: the odyssey of membrane-bound M13 protein\" they illustrate how a large series of spectroscopic techniques have been employed worldwide over a period of more than 20 years to continuously update the structure model of the M13 protein in its membrane-bound form.",
